# Volatile third-party x402 service endpoints (the "moving fast, changes weekly" set).
# These are hackathon and early-startup hosts that flake from CI: timeouts, odd status
# codes, transient connection failures. The directories in the README (Coinbase Bazaar,
# x402scan, Agent402) are the live source of truth for these. Excluded here so that link
# rot on our own links and the stable ecosystem is the only thing that fails the build.
